stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: created in agenda
    pending --> pending: edit (title, description, threshold, key, order)
    pending --> voting_open: openResolution (only when session.state='live')
    voting_open --> voting_open: vote cast / re-cast / late-join
    voting_open --> voting_closed: closeResolution (with confirm-on-incomplete)
    pending --> skipped: syndic explicitly marks information-only
    voting_closed --> [*]
    skipped --> [*]
